canonical:
  title: 老妓
  author: 鄭樞
  language: lzh
  text: 寒燈孤枕淚無窮錦帳銀屛昨夢中以色事人終見棄莫將紈扇怨西風
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 老妓
  author: 鄭樞
  language: lzh
  text: 寒燈孤枕淚無窮。錦帳銀屛昨夢中。以色事人終見棄。莫將紈扇怨西風。
korean:
  title: 노기
  author: 정추
  language: kor
  text: |-
    찬 등불 외로운 베개에 눈물이 끝없나니
    비단 장막 은 병풍은 어젯밤 꿈속이네
    색으로 사람을 섬기면 마침내 버림받거니
    비단부채 서쪽 바람을 원망하지 말라
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0240_010_1120&viewSync=OT
  footnotes:
  - key: '[주-D001] 비단부채 : '
    value: 부채가 여름에는 쓰이다가 가을이 오면 버려지는 것인데, 이것을 젊은 시절에 남자의 사랑을 받다가 나이들면 버림받는 여자에게 비유한 것이다.
english:
  title: The Aging Courtesan
  author: Jeong Chu
  language: eng
  text: |-
    By cold lamplight on a lonely pillow, tears flow without end.
    The silken curtains and silver screens—they were but last night's dream.
    When beauty is the currency of service, abandonment is the price.
    Do not blame the silk fan for the autumn wind.
  footnotes:
  - key: ''
    value: 'The silk fan serves as a metaphor for the courtesan''s fate: just as a fan is cherished in summer but discarded when autumn comes, so too is a woman valued for her beauty in youth but cast aside in age.'
